 Blackpink的Jisoo Inks与Warner Records的独奏职业合作https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpinks-jisoo-inks-partnership-with-warner-records-for-solo-career-3833444?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=blackpinks-jisoo-inks-partnership-与Warner Records for-Solo-CareerCarmen Chin Fri, 31 Jan 2025 10:03:11 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3833444 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/blackpink-jisoo-warner-records-new-partnership-solo-music.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="BlackPink Jisoo Warner记录新的合作伙伴独奏音乐" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/blackpink-jisoo-warner-records-new-partnership-solo-music.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/blackpink-jisoo-warner-records-new-partnership-solo-music-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/blackpink-jisoo-warner-records-new-partnership-solo-music-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/blackpink-jisoo-warner-records-new-partnership-solo-music-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/blackpink-jisoo-warner-records-new-partnership-solo-music-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/blackpink-jisoo-warner-records-new-partnership-solo-music-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 2月14日，她在第一次成为独奏家之前的第一个迷你专辑之前</p><p>BlackPink Post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpinks-jisoo-inks-partnership-with-warner-records-for-solo-career-3833444">BlackPink与Warner Records独奏职业的Jisoo Inks合作伙伴关系</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/blackpink-jisoo-warner-records-new-partnership-solo-music.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="BlackPink Jisoo Warner记录新的合作伙伴独奏音乐" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2