ery similar to the one they <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nirvana-61-1233729">played at the band&#39;s induction into the Rock and Roll Hall Of Fame in 2014</a> , although <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lorde">Lorde</a> performed there instead of Violet Grohl.</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">来自Nirvana的PAT，Krist和Dave的St. Vincent在洛杉矶<a href="https://t.co/qBMQBJQfVY">pic.twitter.com/qbmqbjqfvy</a>举行的“品种”的PAT，Krist和Dave表演。</p><p> -  b面（@bsidestv） <a href="https://twitter.com/BSidesTV/status/1885217451924926651?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2025年1月31日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> Nirvana Reunion feat Kim Gordon “School” <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/fireaid?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#fireaid</a> <a href="https://t.co/2OctbgEvVM">pic.twitter.com/2OctbgEvVM</a></p><p> — Steve Derico (@stevederico) <a href="https://twitter.com/stevederico/status/1885225293990002894?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">January 31, 2025</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Nirvana: Territorial Pissings live FireAid 2025 Ft. Joan Jett [REUNION]" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3-Hag0YRePA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> Dave Grohl&#39;s daughter Violet sings lead, as Kim Gordon plays bass with the surviving members of Nirvana to perform &quot;All Apologies&quot; at the FireAid benefit concert in Los Angeles <a href="https://t.co/PdQOhFAA