<p> Many musicians stepped up to help out the affected communities in the aftermath of the fires. <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonces-foundation-announces-2-5million-donation-to-la-wildfire-relief-3828303">Beyoncé&#39;s BeyGOOD foundation donated $2.5million</a> to help to relief efforts. <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-hilton-launches-fund-for-families-displaced-by-the-la-wildfires-3828081">巴黎·希尔顿（Paris Hilton）还为被大火流离失所的家庭开设了一项基金</a>，承诺要捐款100,000美元，最高可达100,000美元的捐款。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-grohl-spent-birthday-making-meals-for-families-hit-by-la-wildfires-3829226">戴夫·格罗尔（Dave Grohl）还为受到影响的家庭度过了生日</a>。</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-surviving-members-of-nirvana-reunite-with-joan-jett-kim-gordon-and-st-vincent-at-la-fires-benefit-concert-3833434">Watch surviving members of Nirvana reunite with Joan Jett, Kim Gordon and St. Vincent at LA fires benefit concert</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
