rcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_tomgrennan_edcooke_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_tomgrennan_edcooke_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_tomgrennan_edcooke_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_tomgrennan_edcooke_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_tomgrennan_edcooke_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_tomgrennan_edcooke_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-grennan">汤姆·格伦南（Tom Grennan）</a>分享了他欣喜若狂的单曲“ Shadowboxing”，并宣布了“我到处走的地方”的新专辑，这将我带到了我不想成为的地方。在下面查看。</p><p> The new album which is singer-songwriter&#39;s fourth, is set for release on August 15 and can be pre-ordered/pre-saved <a href="https://tomgrennan.lnk.to/EIWLMTWIDWTBPR" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> .</p><p> According to a press release, the record, which was produced by Justin Tranter, who has previously worked with <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/britney-spears">Britney Spears</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/linkin-park">Linkin Park</a> , is “about self-belief and having the confidence to take risks”.</p><p> Grennan added: “This album is about me, revived.现在我在一个想成为的地方。我已经准备好让人们的头脑震惊。”</p><p>您可以在下面收听的新单曲，遵循他的节日单曲“它不能是圣诞节”。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify嵌入：ShadowBoxing" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="152" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/55Ml2qIECJeLRo8qzRnSGO?si=lWX9CRiESVyLn4K9_pf5Ew&#038;context=spotify%3Aalbum%3A1lNgCoCV3uPOfKjHp3R5YD&#038;nd=1&#038;dlsi=b47d9cd652a4456e&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p>汤姆谈到单曲时说：“它代表了整张专辑的目的。” “这是关于我与我的一面战斗，我遇到了很多麻烦。这仍然是日常战斗。但是我学会了如何与所有这些恶魔作斗争，现在我在心理和身体上做好了准备。我处于运动员模式。”</p><p> The album tracklisting for &#39;Everywhere I Went Led Me To Where I Don&#39;t Want To Be&#39; is:</p><p> <strong>&#39;Full Attention&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Cool With That&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Shadowboxing&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Boys Don&#39;t Cry&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Somewhere Only We Go&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Shadows On The Ceiling&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;庆祝&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;更高&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Certified&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;钻石&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Dirty Dishes&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;肉桂&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Drama Queen&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;I Won&#39;t Miss A Thing&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Lonely Dancer&#39;</strong></p><p>这位歌手兼作曲家还在9月3日在伯恩茅斯（Bournemouth）举行的英国和爱尔兰巡回赛巡回演出，并于9月6日在伦敦的O2竞技场举行了一场演出，然后于9月19日在曼彻斯特结束。</p><p>汤姆·格伦南（Tom Grennan）在星期二（2月4日）下午3点之前预订汤姆·格伦南（Tom Grennan）的新专辑的粉丝将在第二天（2月5日）上午10点获得预售的独家访问权，可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Ftom-grennan-tickets%2Fartist%2F5211869" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买。门票将在下周五（2月7日）上午10点进行一般销售，可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Ftom-grennan-tickets%2Fartist%2F5211869" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>购买。</p><h2><strong>汤姆·格伦南（Tom Grennan）将参加：</strong></h2><p><strong>九月</strong><br /><strong>3  - 伯恩茅斯 -  BIC</strong><br /> <strong>4  - 伯明翰 -  Utilita Arena</strong><br /> <strong>6  - 伦敦 -  O2</strong><br /> <strong>9  - 加的夫 -  Utilita Arena</strong><br /> <strong>10  - 诺丁汉 - 电动点竞技场</strong><br /><strong>11  - 格拉斯哥 -  OVO Hydro</strong><br /> <strong>13  - 都柏林 -  3arena</strong><br /> <strong>15  - 阿伯丁 -  P＆J竞技场</strong><br /><strong>16  - 纽卡斯尔 -  Utilita Arena</strong><br /> <strong>18  - 利兹 - 第一个直接竞技场</strong><br /><strong>19  - 曼彻斯特 - 合作现场</strong></p